STATUS PAGE
===========

- SD:   ok (x files)   / not found
- Link: ok (x peers)   / not found
- MIDI: ok / no device / not found 

- PLAYING: 03_super.mp3 (x:xx / x:xx)

- MEDIA SELECT: 03_super.mp3

A: short= prev  long= menu page
B: short= play  long= stop
C: short= next  



MENU PAGE
=========

+ Audio Out
    ++ Internal
    ++ Last saved BT
    ++ Detected BT1
    ++ Detected BT2
    ++ ... (list available BT devices)

+ OTA Update (connect to hmsphr)
    -> page with progress bar



